description:
Public release of a version of the cross-reference capability of the UBID software that is
feature-limited to cross-reference via Jaccard similarity coefficient (viz., intersection-over-union or "IoU") [2] over a
quadtree-based spatial index only.
name: Unique Building Identifier (UBID) cross-reference using intersection-over-union (IoU) over quadtreebased spatial index
